&lt;p&gt;入院后查相关检查以明确诊断。先后给予阿托伐他汀钙片口服以调脂治疗，阿司匹林肠溶片口服以抗血小板凝集治疗，&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: 楷体_GB2312;'&gt;奥扎格雷钠80毫克/次，日1次静点以降纤治疗，胞磷胆碱钠注射液0.75克/次，日1次静点以营养神经治疗，厄贝沙坦氢氯噻嗪分散片1片/次，日1次口服及牛黄降压丸1.6克/次，日1次口服以降压治疗，中药《血府逐瘀汤加减方》以活血化瘀、通络治疗，中医针灸以疏通经络止痛治疗，洛索洛芬钠片1片/次，日2次口服以止痛治疗，普拉洛芬滴眼液 &amp;nbsp;0.2ml &amp;nbsp;4次/日，点眼 及温湿毛巾外敷眼部。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: 楷体_GB2312;'&gt;住院15&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: 楷体_GB2312;'&gt;天，患者痊愈出院。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;